			<p>This salad looks delicious! I can&#8217;t wait to try it. On a side note, those serrano peppers you have pictured there &#8230; I had my husband run to the store to pick up a few jalapenos, cream cheese, and bacon for your other recipe. He came back with these somewhat thinner than normal jalapenos. Not wanting to be ungrateful, I used them.</p>
<p>They weren&#8217;t bad flavor-wise but good lord! The red, hot, burning rash of hot pepper juice went from my fingertips to half way down each finger and no matter how many times I washed my hands, it remained.</p>
<p>If I couldn&#8217;t tell the difference before, I sure can now. Some things are, literally, burned into memory.</p>
