			<p>I can&#8217;t stand coriander/cilantro either but have made a similar noodle salad to this with Lemon Basil instead (which is heavenly) or a mixture of basil and mint if I can&#8217;t get Lemon Basil (which is very easy to grow) </p>
<p>I serve mine with thinly sliced duck breast or smoked chicken. Heavenly. And if you are dishing this up to the hungry types (cowboys included) then handing them each a big chinese pancake (like you get with Peking Duck) and slapping a serving in that &#8211; it generally goes down well! The kids love it; the messier the better.</p>
